    "content": "<p>（老手请绕过）<br />\n此教程使用ZateL脚本添加技能过程<br />\n1、添加技能<br />\n首先需要编写技能文件</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"411\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/05/1_yK9WDLr.jpg\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p>然后添加技能文件加上对应编号</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"408\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/05/2_2fzSvLl.jpg\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p>最后在技能树上显示</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"313\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/05/3_uze1EjG.jpg\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p>没有设置NUT的话技能可以学,但是进图是灰色的</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"609\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/05/4_WygpdUS.jpg\" width=\"798\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"153\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/05/5_9F5noJx.jpg\" width=\"333\" /></p>\n\n<p>第二添加NUT<br />\n大部分萌新灰技能，冲突，各种bug就出在这里<br />\nZateL佬的两个文件分别是执行文件和状态数据文件（我的理解）<br />\n[zskill00.nut]判断是否执行动作，添加状态等等<br />\n[thief_header.nut]申明技能状态、技能编号、ANI指向编号、ATK指向编号<br />\n添加到thief_load_state.nut<img alt=\"\" height=\"294\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/05/6_yFUPZsM.jpg\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"489\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/05/7_3TFRKBg.jpg\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p>保存上传跑五国技能可以用了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n技能执行文件细节</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"612\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/05/8_0XyJWok.jpg\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p>状态数据文件细节</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"945\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/05/9_EDmT0d0.jpg\" width=\"900\" /></p>\n\n<p>使用成功</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"525\" src=\"/media/uploads/2023/07/05/10.gif\" width=\"700\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><span style=\"font-size:26px\">有用的评论</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.d537d52f.937UeX_DOAcwWwZkMAgeqA&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;fr=pb\" target=\"_blank\">憨批老王</a>:&nbsp;楼主有研究过如何在空中放技能吗<img alt=\"\" height=\"30\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon25.png\" width=\"30\" /></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.147ac975.sIuHaqzgrE7wbCx2YqLXpw&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;fr=pb\" target=\"_blank\">冰泪空</a>:&nbsp;回复&nbsp;<a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?un=%E6%86%A8%E6%89%B9%E8%80%81%E7%8E%8B&amp;fr=pb&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;id=tb.1.d537d52f.937UeX_DOAcwWwZkMAgeqA\" onclick=\"Stats.sendRequest('fr=tb0_forum&amp;st_mod=pb&amp;st_value=atlink');\" target=\"_blank\">憨批老王</a>&nbsp;:最近才研究的，没太深入<img alt=\"\" height=\"30\" src=\"https://tb2.bdstatic.com/tb/editor/images/face/i_f18.png?t=20140803\" width=\"30\" /></li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.d537d52f.937UeX_DOAcwWwZkMAgeqA&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;fr=pb\" target=\"_blank\">憨批老王</a>:&nbsp;我目前卡在这了，怎么写都没法在空中点亮技能<img alt=\"\" height=\"30\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon6.png\" width=\"30\" /></li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p><a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.99806b66.RR2dxZz-aR_VLq0YAAPoew&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;fr=pb\" target=\"_blank\">Elesc</a>:&nbsp;回复 憨批老王 :local skill = sq_GetSkill(obj, 101);//获取技能编号101 skill.setCommandEnable(true);//设置技能点亮101 再加个Z轴判断大于0就行了了，加在 procAppend里<img alt=\"\" height=\"30\" src=\"https://tb2.bdstatic.com/tb/editor/images/face/i_f25.png?t=20140803\" width=\"30\" /></p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"30\" src=\"https://gsp0.baidu.com/5aAHeD3nKhI2p27j8IqW0jdnxx1xbK/tb/editor/images/client/image_emoticon1.png\" width=\"30\" />nut可以本地运行，不需要跑五国的。</p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n",
